OL,5, The Taliban have ordered hair and      
OL,6, beauty salons in Afghanistan to shut in
OL,7, the latest restriction faced by women. 
OL,9,FA Vice and Virtue Ministry spokesman   
OL,10,Ftold the BBC businesses had one month  
OL,11,Fto comply, starting from 2 July when   
OL,12,Fthey were first informed of the move.  
OL,14,FWomen's freedoms have steadily shrunk  
OL,15,Fsince the Taliban seized power in 2021.
OL,17,FThey have barred teenage girls and     
OL,18,Fwomen from classrooms, gyms and parks, 
OL,19,Fand most recently even banned them from
OL,20,Fworking for the United Nations.        
